    "headline": "Align Technology (NASDAQ:ALGN) Surprises With Q1 CY2026 Sales",
    "summary": "Dental technology company Align Technology (NASDAQ:ALGN) reported Q1 CY2026 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 6.2% year on year to $1.04 billion. The company expects next quarter’s revenue to be around $1.05 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.58 per share was 12.8% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
